org.middleheaven.core.wiring
Class BeanDependencyModel

java.lang.Object
  org.middleheaven.core.wiring.BeanDependencyModel

public class BeanDependencyModel
extends java.lang.Object

A model for wiring. The wiring model consists of construct-point where the object is created/retrieved and multiple after-points where the object is injected.
